<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">它们仅在服务器/世界运行时计时，即使暂停亦然</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph>语法：</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">stopwatch &lt;id&gt; create</TextBox> - 使用给定的命名空间 ID 创建一个秒表</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">stopwatch &lt;id&gt; query</TextBox> - 在聊天中显示指定秒表的已用时间（以秒为单位）</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">stopwatch &lt;id&gt; restart</TextBox> - 重启指定秒表</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">stopwatch &lt;id&gt; remove</TextBox> - 删除指定秒表</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Section Style="{StaticResource devnoteQuote}">
  <Paragraph FontWeight="Bold">
    开发者注释
    <Paragraph.Foreground>
      <Binding Path="BorderBrush" RelativeSource="{RelativeSource Mode=FindAncestor, AncestorType=Section}" />
    </Paragraph.Foreground>
  </Paragraph>
  
<Paragraph> 该命令用于取代使用世界边界来记录真实时间的需求。我们计划在后续快照中让世界边界依赖于游戏刻。如果你之前依赖这种方式来衡量真实时间的流逝，请切换到使用新命令，如有任何不符合预期之处请告知。谢谢！</Paragraph>

</Section><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">execute</TextBox></Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">增加了语法 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">/execute if|unless stopwatch &lt;id&gt; &lt;range&gt;</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">允许将给定 Stopwatch 的经过时间与一个浮点值区间进行比较</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">Stopwatch 的数值以秒为单位，精度最高可达毫秒</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">示例：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">/execute if stopwatch foo:bar ..10 run say Stopwatch foo:bar has not reached 10 seconds yet</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">物品组件</Paragraph><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">增加了 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">minecraft:use_effects</TextBox></Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">控制玩家在使用物品（鼠标右键）时的行为</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">格式：对象，字段如下</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">can_sprint</TextBox>: 布尔值，玩家在使用该物品时是否可以疾跑</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">false</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">speed_multiplier</TextBox>: 浮点数（0 到 1），玩家在使用该物品时应用的速度倍率</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">0.2</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">例如：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">use_effects={can_sprint:true,speed_multiplier:1.0}</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">增加了 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">minecraft:minimum_attack_charge</TextBox></Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">设定用该物品进行攻击所需的最小攻击指示器蓄力</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">格式：浮点数（0.0 到 1.0）</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">0.0：无需蓄力</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">1.0：需要满蓄力</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">增加了 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">minecraft:damage_type</TextBox></Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">指定该物品造成的伤害类型</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">格式：字符串，伤害类型标识符</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">例如：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">damage_type=&apos;minecraft:spear&apos;</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">增加了 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">minecraft:kinetic_weapon</TextBox></Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">在使用该物品时（主要用于矛）启用 Charge 类攻击：在使用期间，每刻沿一条射线基于实体的相对速度造成伤害</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">格式：对象，字段如下</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">min_reach</TextBox>: 浮点数，从攻击者到目标的以格数计的最小有效距离</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">0.0</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">max_reach</TextBox>: 浮点数，从攻击者到目标的以格数计的最大有效距离</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">3.0</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">hitbox_margin</TextBox>: 浮点数，检测有效碰撞时应用于目标边界框的余量</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">0.3</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">delay_ticks</TextBox>: 整数，武器生效前所需的刻数</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">0</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">dismount_conditions</TextBox>、<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">knockback_conditions</TextBox>、<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">damage_conditions</TextBox>：分别指示何时应用取消骑乘、击退与伤害效果的条件。为对象，包含：</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">max_duration_ticks</TextBox>: 整数，超过该刻数后将不再检查条件。该计时自 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">delay</TextBox> 结束后开始</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">min_speed</TextBox>: 浮点数，攻击者沿其视线方向的以每秒格数计的最小速度</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可选，默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">0.0</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">min_relative_speed</TextBox>: 浮点数，攻击者与目标之间沿攻击者视线方向的以每秒格数计的最小相对速度</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可选，默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">0.0</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">forward_movement</TextBox>: 浮点数，动画期间物品自手中向前移动的距离</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">0.0</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">damage_multiplier</TextBox>: 浮点数，相对速度换算为最终伤害的倍率</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">1.0</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">sound</TextBox>: 可选 声音事件，在武器进入 Charge 状态时播放</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">hit_sound</TextBox>: 可选 声音事件，在武器击中实体时播放</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">例如：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">kinetic_weapon={max_reach:5.0,forward_movement:1.0,delay:20,damage_conditions:{max_duration:60},knockback_conditions:{max_duration:40},dismount_conditions:{max_duration:20}}</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">造成的伤害计算为 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">floor(relative_speed * velocity_multiplier)</TextBox>，其中 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">relative_speed</TextBox> 为攻击者与目标速度向量在攻击者视线向量轴上的投影之差</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">附魔或属性修饰带来的额外伤害在该计算之后再叠加</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">增加了 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">minecraft:piercing_weapon</TextBox></Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">启用一次快速攻击，沿一条射线伤害多个实体（主要用于矛）</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">格式：对象，字段如下</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">min_reach</TextBox>、<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">max_reach</TextBox>、<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">hitbox_margin</TextBox>：同 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">kinetic_weapon</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">deals_knockback</TextBox>: 布尔值，攻击是否会造成击退</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">true</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">dismounts</TextBox>: 布尔值，攻击是否会令目标卸下骑乘</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">默认值：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">false</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">sound</TextBox>: 可选，声音事件，在玩家使用该武器攻击时播放</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">hit_sound</TextBox>: 可选，声音事件，在武器击中实体时播放</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">例如：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">piercing_weapon={min_reach:0,max_reach:4,dismounts:true}</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">增加了 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">minecraft:swing_animation</TextBox></Paragraph><List>
